  "texts": [
    "In contrast, our proposed blockchain-powered framework offers a practical solution that links and governs the data mesh's independent domains and products.",
    "Both the data mesh and blockchain are fundamentally decentralized.",
    "This core similarity makes blockchain technology a perfect fit to support the data mesh principles and solves its decentralization challenges.",
    "Dataset ManagementThere has been a variety of research work that focused on managing datasets.",
    "On a conceptual level, authors in [31] envisioned an ecosystem, namely Agora, to provide access to data pipeline assets, such as data, algorithms, and computing resources, through marketplaces focusing on these assets as core components."
